        <abstract> 
<p>Sends details of the progress of his researches for <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>His son Leonard will photograph Elston and Cleatham. He has found an early drawing of Elston.</p>
            <p>Asks for a letter of introduction for Leonard Darwin to CMCD’s tenant at Elston.</p>
